{"tid":1557804,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[終極對決]余黎青萍定伍淑清樣衰D","createTime":"2019-09-10T09:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T09:44:08.000Z","uid":49197,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6158533987c11b39c9038792f6f4ebafc2888bb9","tid":1557804,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:12:51.000Z","msg":"雖然林鄭 梁愛詩 葉劉呢班奶共柒頭係樣衰,但公道D講,我覺得佢地樣衰極都有廿幾三十分,而最近開始多人識既余黎青萍同伍淑清就真係挑戰緊香港市民既審美下限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20190628/s00006/05b770eeaabb2ce2bb2c3321d547bfa2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20190628%2Fs00006%2F05b770eeaabb2ce2bb2c3321d547bfa2.jpg&h=65a79c91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20130528/photo/0528-00407-011b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20130528%2Fphoto%2F0528-00407-011b1.jpg&h=092f0054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n余黎青萍特色<br />\n1)面無四兩肉<br />\n2)扁口扁面<br />\n3)個頭發育不良咁,細到唔啱比例<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://elite.youth.cn/qlk/201310/W020131021598542425167.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Felite.youth.cn%2Fqlk%2F201310%2FW020131021598542425167.jpg&h=f06a77ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5d735bcf0062511817a9a0ac.jpg/6VvHD5SyjzQo2pBfJfD81Eqdzhlv79ZEGmIzRBpiM0Q?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5d735bcf0062511817a9a0ac.jpg%2F6VvHD5SyjzQo2pBfJfD81Eqdzhlv79ZEGmIzRBpiM0Q%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=bd2d114d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1)惡形惡相<br />\n2)好似時刻感覺高人一等咁<br />\n3)最早奶共既柒頭之一,求其搵下佢D新聞都睇倒佢已經奶到不顧廉恥既地步<br />\n3)一生無嫁過,可能格真係衰到無人頂得順,睇錢份上都唔制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就覺得伍淑清樣衰好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />余麗青萍都仲有十幾廿分,個咩伍淑清個樣真係好撚核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,想比0分"},{"pid":"af025d0e7f33a67a8072da7d208dd739184338fd","tid":1557804,"uid":56432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:14:46.000Z","msg":"樣子幾醜都唔夠奶共行為醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3dceb29cdca9b63777069f029a7d61aa7aeca47","tid":1557804,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af025d0e7f33a67a8072da7d208dd739184338fd","tid":1557804,"uid":56432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:14:46.000Z","msg":"樣子幾醜都唔夠奶共行為醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:15:22.000Z","msg":"通常奶得多個面相都會越黎越衰"},{"pid":"08cebf52fa6659522bd25a0f6e5740c42aac8a43","tid":1557804,"uid":13616,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:18:09.000Z","msg":"譚惠珠一出<br />\n上面兩個都要彈開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講還講唔好貼相"},{"pid":"a968e7e6106a9a5f90a1e750b04d18a17f98652d","tid":1557804,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:19:32.000Z","msg":"屌你老尾！玩豬肉算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://gss0.baidu.com/-4o3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy/zhidao/pic/item/a8ec8a13632762d00392a203a5ec08fa503dc6da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgss0.baidu.com%2F-4o3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy%2Fzhidao%2Fpic%2Fitem%2Fa8ec8a13632762d00392a203a5ec08fa503dc6da.jpg&h=0cd50f3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfa283a2e742f4b6fdf716